BUDGET; HOUSING -- UNITED STATES; LOW INCOME HOUSING; POLITICAL ACTIVISM; 
UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT; COMMUNITY FOR CREATIVE NONVIOLENCE; NATIONAL 
COALITION FOR THE HOMELESS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
