<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEW FEATURE SCANS THE LOCAL ECONOMY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Starting today, The Times will include up-to-date economic information about 
Ventura County each Monday in a Business section feature called The Numbers. 
</P>
<P>
Statistics on subjects including the local Consumer Price Index and the cost of 
housing will be presented as part of the Times' ongoing economic survey of 
Southern California. 
</P>
</TEXT>
