in the ninth gave the Padres the winning edge over the Giants. Associated 
Press; Photo, After the Padres took a 4-3 lead in the ninth, Bip Roberts, 
right, singled, advanced to third and was greeted by Coach Sandy Alomar. 
Associated Press 
</P>
